name: The Paddock
description: We all played on the wasteland, behind the old estate, it was safer than in the confines of the complex, nobody trying to hurt you, there wasn't much there, but we would all play till it was time to go home, one by one the kids would go home to their suppers, all but Jane. Jane would stay and dream under the old chestnut tree until long after dark, wearily making her way home eventually.
